XoZq_j.png","title":"Hake Salad with Mango and Lime Mayonnaise","publishedAt":"2016-08-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"31.4 g","fat":"35.5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13.5 g","calories":"2086 kJ \/ 499 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking tray, wire rack, serving bowl, jug, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","40m","4 portions"]}